How to Buy

  • 1 - Buy and Hold (DEX)

    To buy on Solana, go to Birdeye (click here!) and connect your Phantom or other Solana wallet. Swap SOL, USDT, BONK or other to purchase $SMOG tokens. Hold them to qualify for the airdrop! We'll detect this and start tracking your airdrop points.

  • 2 - Buy and Stake (OTC)

    Use our OTC widget at the top of this page to purchase $SMOG on Ethereum at a 10% discount and stake to earn APY. Staked tokens are locked for 90 days. You'll also qualify for the airdrop!

  • 3 - Signup to the Airdrop

    Join the Smog community on Zealy to earn extra points that will contribute towards the $SMOG airdrop. The more tasks you complete, the more points youll earn! These points will be updated a few weeks after launch.
